version_description: This is an acoustic simplified version for novice guitar players.
Includes all correct chords and inversions, as well as a tab of the riff. No capo.

This is pretty much exactly how the song goes, all credit goes to ExplodingHat, he posted this in a comment on another tab but it was never officially posted, but this way you can hover over all the chords and all that jazz.
Open E and A strings are intentional - let them ring for the deep acoustic sound .
Full chord tab of the song using chords Chris plays live on Youtube videos. Includes strum pattern and bpm timing.
Song: Imagine (John Lennon cover) Artist: Chris Cornell Album: Songbook Year: 2011 Youtube: https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=Wgll3iLF1jk.
